  "rationale": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice C is correct.&nbsp;It's given that function <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"g\"><mi>g</mi></math> is defined by <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"g left parenthesis x right parenthesis equals StartRoot x EndRoot plus 300\"><mi>g</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mi>x</mi></msqrt><mo>+</mo><mn>300</mn></math>. Substituting <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"81\"><mn>81</mn></math> for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x\"><mi>x</mi></math> in function <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"g\"><mi>g</mi></math> yields&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"g left parenthesis 81 right parenthesis equals StartRoot 81 EndRoot plus 300\"><mi>g</mi><mo>(</mo><mn>81</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>81</mn></msqrt><mo>+</mo><mn>300</mn></math>, which is equivalent to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"g left parenthesis 81 right parenthesis equals 9 plus 300\"><mi>g</mi><mo>(</mo><mn>81</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>300</mn></math>, or <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"g left parenthesis 81 right parenthesis equals 309\"><mi>g</mi><mo>(</mo><mn>81</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>309</mn></math>. Therefore, the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"g left parenthesis x right parenthesis\"><mi>g</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo></math> when <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"x equals 81\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>81</mn></math> is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"309\"><mn>309</mn></math>.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice A is incorrect. This is the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"StartRoot 81 EndRoot\"><msqrt><mn>81</mn></msqrt></math>, not <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"StartRoot 81 EndRoot plus 300\"><msqrt><mn>81</mn></msqrt><mo>+</mo><mn>300</mn></math>.</p>\n<p>Choice B is incorrect and may result from conceptual or calculation errors.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Choice D is incorrect. This is the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"81 plus 300\"><mn>81</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>300</mn></math>, not <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"StartRoot 81 EndRoot plus 300\"><msqrt><mn>81</mn></msqrt><mo>+</mo><mn>300</mn></math>.</p>",
